[38;2;253;151;31m###[0m[38;2;253;151;31m [0m[38;2;253;151;31mPurpose and Goals[0m

[38;2;255;255;255mThe purpose of this project is to create an engaging and interactive platform for users to challenge themselve[0m
[38;2;255;255;255ms and enhance their knowledge on a particular subject. The goals of the project include:[0m

[38;2;255;255;255m1[0m[38;2;119;119;119m.[0m[38;2;255;255;255m [0m[1;38;2;249;38;114m**[0m[1;38;2;249;38;114mInteractive Learning:[0m[1;38;2;249;38;114m**[0m[38;2;255;255;255m Offer users an opportunity to learn and have fun at the same time by answering qu[0m
