[38;2;255;255;255m5[0m[38;2;119;119;119m.[0m[38;2;255;255;255m [0m[1;38;2;249;38;114m**[0m[1;38;2;249;38;114mExpandability:[0m[1;38;2;249;38;114m**[0m[38;2;255;255;255m Create a foundation for further development, such as adding more questions, topics, or a[0m
[38;2;255;255;255mdditional features like hints or explanations.[0m

